---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Tomato Problems - Home Grown Tomatoes" description="Troubleshooting guides for common tomato plant problems." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />

		<main class="page">
			<h1>Tomato Problems</h1>
			<p>Identify and fix common tomato plant problems before they ruin your harvest.</p>

			<h2>Common Problems</h2>

			<ul>
				<li>Why Tomato Leaves Turn Yellow</li>
				<li>Blossom End Rot</li>
				<li>Tomato Blight</li>
				<li>Leaf Curl</li>
				<li>Cracked Tomatoes</li>
				<li>Pests on Tomato Plants</li>
			</ul>

			<p>These guides will help you understand what is happening and what to do next.</p>
		</main>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.page {
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 80px auto;
		padding: 20px;
	}
</style>